OL,3,CNearly three years in prison for carer
OL,4,Cwho stole pensioner's life savings
OL,6,FA care worker who stole thousands of
OL,7,Fpounds from a vulnerable pensioner she
OL,8,Fwas caring for has been sentenced to
OL,9,Ftwo years and nine months in prison in
OL,10,FJersey's Royal Court.
OL,12,FSandra Natalie Jardim De Sousa, 43,
OL,13,Fused the bank cards of her 80-year-old
OL,14,Fvictim to purchase several luxury
OL,15,Fitems, including a smart watch and a
OL,16,Fvacuum cleaner.
OL,18,FShe was found guilty of stealing from
OL,19,Fthe pensioner in May.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
