OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1782564485
OL,3,CNearly three years in prison for carer
OL,4,Cwho stole pensioner's life savings
OL,6,FDe Sousa was brought to the Jersey
OL,7,FRoyal Court from custody today
OL,8,F(Wednesday 24 June).
OL,10,FThe court heard how, over the period
OL,11,Fof five months, she stole more than
OL,12,F#8,000 from her victim, leaving them
OL,13,Fwith just #19 in her account.
OL,15,FThe prosecution told the court that De
OL,16,FSousa's crimes were selfish, callous
OL,17,Fand exploitative. They also spoke of
OL,18,Fhow the vulnerable pensioner placed
OL,19,Fenormous trust in her.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1782564485
OL,3,CNearly three years in prison for carer
OL,4,Cwho stole pensioner's life savings
OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, the victim's
OL,7,Ffamily released a statement saying:
OL,8,F"While today's outcome brings some
OL,9,Fmeasure of justice, no sentence can
OL,10,Ffully reflect the far-reaching impact
OL,11,Fthis has had on our family and the
OL,12,Ftrust that has been lost.
OL,14,F"We hope this case serves as a
OL,15,Freminder of the importance of
OL,16,Fprotecting vulnerable people and
OL,17,Fholding those in positions of trust
OL,18,Faccountable for their actions."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
